      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it has been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures! It drives smoothly and is super comfortable for daily commutes or weekend getaways. If you're looking for a great ride that\u2019s been loved and looked after, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
