      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This example is mechanically robust, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a recently overhauled cooling system including a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. Suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the chassis maintains its communicative feedback. A driver-focused machine ready for spirited canyon carving or track duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
