    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained executive sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliable performance. The exterior features a deep, lustrous metallic finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only the minor, superficial road wear expected of a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of cracks or tears, and the genuine wood trim retains its original glow. All electronic features, including the high-fidelity sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having followed a strict manufacturer-recommended service schedule. Recent updates include a new set of high-performance all-season tires and a fresh brake service. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, and the transmission shifts imperceptibly. It has been kept in a smoke-free environment and comes with a complete set of owner's manuals and two remote key fobs. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy the premium driving experience it provides.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for those seeking mechanical reliability and refined presentation. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous professional evaluation, confirming its structural integrity and consistent performance. Offering a sophisticated balance of luxury and utility, this vehicle stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains in commendable aesthetic form. We invite serious inquiries to experience a specimen that delivers both prestige and peace of mind.",
